OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy for most to start the
OL,6,Fday with showers. Turning drier with
OL,7,Fsunny spells in the afternoon as
OL,8,Fshowers becoming more isolated.
OL,9,FRemaining warm for the time of year.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny showers fading by the
OL,12,Fevening with cloudy periods to follow.
OL,13,FCloud thickening by the second half of
OL,14,Fthe night with rain approaching from
OL,15,Fthe west.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA grey and wet start for some.
OL,18,FRain becoming widespread across the
OL,19,Farea with heavy outbreaks possible
OL,20,Fduring the afternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
